Ami akpọ usen ye friends mi ke English and Ibibio combined.

Sometimes nyin akpa conversation entirely in Pidgin-Ibibio mix.
Nnyin akpọ ‘good morning’ before akam ‘mmon’.
Teacher mi emi say, ‘you must speak Ibibio correctly’.
